<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" author="Brandon Kiem" dateTime="2021-06-21T16:09:00" id="_0ce1b53f-d308-4dd4-936b-45fa5f344245" outputclass="ncc-clause" type="insert"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>J3D10</sptc><title id="_e0746567-c898-483d-9b35-f7c317319bdf">Floors of a Class 4 part of a building</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_80244019-5686-4c05-b63e-8c61b60a15aa" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_5a868431-a1fb-47c3-8144-d549a7fe61a7">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Where a Class 4 part of a building has a concrete floor above an unenclosed <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1213_1.0.0.xml#_8dacd66d-0556-4df9-bd71-3983532ec002" id="_c2c425b0-7883-4a22-8cfe-8d5d923cb89c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">carpark</xref>, undercroft or the like, underfloor insulation must be installed with an <xref xmlns:qxa="urn:schemas-quark-com:xmlauthor" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1420_0.4.0.xml#_f438bdfd-6adb-43c4-b342-7b1656af23c4" id="_a449dccb-6f35-4560-97ab-0572993086d1" qxa:read-only="true" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="true" type="glossterm">R-Value</xref> at least—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_88a17efe-f9ff-4e5e-88ed-61848ddc358e">in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_be1fb943-991e-4ff3-a050-5e55eea8a3bc" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zone</xref> 2 and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_da652ed8-6e92-4c54-834e-3459df95f3c3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zones</xref> 5 to 8, R2.0; and</li><li id="_99f3c701-be0a-4b77-a190-9b8ac2245506">in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_26532a59-b61b-412f-bb2a-6e9be2e85f52" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zones</xref> 3 and 4, R1.5.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_4b92fcff-eb05-4a90-8438-d45b10f19cbf" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_dabf0ed3-f48b-4efa-8ec6-324e38130e77">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Where a Class 4 part of a building has a concrete floor above an enclosed <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1213_1.0.0.xml#_8dacd66d-0556-4df9-bd71-3983532ec002" id="_b9dc6f4b-f86d-49bd-8e35-87e6f30c0c4f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">carpark</xref>, undercroft or the like, underfloor insulation must be installed with an <xref xmlns:qxa="urn:schemas-quark-com:xmlauthor" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1420_0.4.0.xml#_f438bdfd-6adb-43c4-b342-7b1656af23c4" id="_56bc1c88-f31c-4a58-a3e3-9201ae2584f4" qxa:read-only="true" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="true" type="glossterm">R-Value</xref> at least—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_ca497f01-f2aa-4e39-977d-4b717f737c53">in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_b3ba76ae-ebfe-4487-9de4-0e28ae911895" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zone</xref> 2, R0.5; and</li><li id="_24132be1-a4c2-4a1d-aff1-dccf730a473a">in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_1dd9bb39-7bbb-459b-8acc-2bf76c2d26aa" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zones</xref> 4 and 5, R1.0; and</li><li id="_fd64f3e1-9824-4e0b-9694-fe0514559485">in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_6072828a-8766-41cc-a9b8-1ab30c653869" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zone</xref> 6, R1.5; and</li><li id="_c7d8cfb5-8b4b-4062-bb42-61f57e65a554">in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_58b93826-12bc-41ad-ab0d-bd103756bdca" id="_7c291a12-5e4a-4b9c-881b-126e6086de2d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">climate zones</xref> 7 and 8, R2.0.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_c8bd15f6-cb64-4d6e-8a3f-ce0ffab2bba3" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_28b46231-5525-405c-ad85-b57097df1529">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>A concrete slab-on-ground, including a waffle-pod slab, with an in-slab or in-screed heating or cooling system must have insulation with an <xref xmlns:qxa="urn:schemas-quark-com:xmlauthor" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1420_0.4.0.xml#_f438bdfd-6adb-43c4-b342-7b1656af23c4" id="_c712f20f-5f90-4f77-8ed9-5d2e864ef9b5" qxa:read-only="true" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="true" type="glossterm">R-Value</xref> at least 1.0 installed around the vertical edge of its perimeter.</p></subclause><subclause id="_aeff6d18-4ed5-4919-9d55-893bda583393" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_6ff3c57c-ee9e-4268-b36d-da0854a2e666">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>A concrete slab-on-ground, other than a waffle-pod slab, must be insulated in accordance with the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_c18af7a4-4279-41bb-841a-c551f31d151a">In <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_41829a45-3abc-4153-bdd2-a69fbf638c4c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 6 and 7—<ol><li>insulation with an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_705a6a31-8dfa-42ed-b612-2c81f803fd89" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of at least 0.64 must be installed around the vertical edge of its perimeter; and</li><li>insulation with an <xref xmlns:qxa="urn:schemas-quark-com:xmlauthor" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1420_0.4.0.xml#_f438bdfd-6adb-43c4-b342-7b1656af23c4" id="_b562be21-755c-4db0-9d8b-7190685d6649" qxa:read-only="true" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="true" type="glossterm">R-Value</xref> of at least 0.64 must be installed underneath the slab.</li></ol></li><li id="_c9eed2e6-e462-47dc-9bce-c3e4968315d7">In <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_ec54556e-8640-4570-8369-7492730d3d4a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zone</xref> 8— <ol><li>insulation with an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_b4682862-8523-4893-b23d-0f934de59d70" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of at least 1.0 must be installed around the vertical edge of its perimeter; and</li><li>insulation with an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_e6cbfb55-56f6-4b3f-881c-66c6e54a32f9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of at least 2.0 must be installed underneath the slab.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_25846dd8-b479-4d8f-8f13-15bb144126ca" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_479c1c92-6c0b-4914-a5fd-52f297def4aa">SubClause</title><num>5</num><p>Insulation <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_a5b45a91-1ac3-44a8-8644-acfc09c225a9" id="_dcba6da3-28c9-45bc-a4e4-802f3a9da705" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">required</xref> by (3), (4)(a)(i) and (4)(b)(i) must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_3cd4ca77-c6ac-4b58-ac49-df3a3a1c7c29">be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1520_0.5.0.xml#_7fe7217d-98de-4375-9395-69b6bfcceec8" id="_cbe8ec6a-fd9a-487b-b594-d37452e3003b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">water resistant</xref>; and</li><li id="_07ac31a0-7cce-43d2-b9f0-2f01c7ea8b4e">be continuous from the adjacent finished ground level—<ol><li>to a depth of not less than 300 mm; or</li><li>for at least the full depth of the vertical edge of the concrete slab-on-ground.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_a05ff779-3920-4c4a-9ee4-041c171053e7" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ff7af9f6-f789-4b59-9369-1b549963abef">SubClause</title><num>6</num><p>The requirements of (3) do not apply to an in-screed heating or cooling system used solely in a bathroom, amenity area or the like.</p></subclause></clause>